replies.body:
Hey I'm glad you like it! 

We actually looked into spectating from your phone back in the day and found out we'd basically need to run a game of League on your phone to make that happen. o_o;;

But, it's been a while since I've been on that team and things have probably changed since then (replays are now a thing, for example, they didn't exist back when the app launched). I can definitely see why it would be cool for players, but I can't say whether or not it will happen. I agree that I think there are some things we could add to the app to make it even cooler though.
